sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant DB as SQLite (alerts)
  participant IM as incident_manager
  participant LK as AlertIncidentLink
  participant WA as watcher (main)
  participant IV as Investigation store
  IM->>DB: read active alerts
  IM->>IM: compute correlation_key (host + category + window)
  alt matches existing incident
    IM->>LK: link alert to incident (confidence)
  else new incident
    IM->>DB: create Incident (status=open)
    IM->>LK: link alert (confidence=high)
  end
  WA->>DB: detect incident needing response
  WA->>IV: create Investigation (status=pending, incident_id, asset_id)
  IV-->>WA: investigation id
  WA->>IV: enqueue for AI analysis
